023/**
024 * A subclass of HTML elements that contain text only.
025 *
026 * <h5 class='section'>See Also:</h5><ul>
027 *    <li class='link'><a class="doclink" href="https://juneau.apache.org/docs/topics/JuneauBeanHtml5">juneau-bean-html5</a>
028 * </ul>
029 */
030@FluentSetters
031public class HtmlElementText extends HtmlElement {
032
033   private Object text;
034
035   /**
036    * Returns the inner text of this element.
037    *
038    * @return The inner text of this element, or <jk>null</jk> if no text is set.
039    */
040   @Xml(format=XmlFormat.TEXT)
041   @Beanp("c")
042   public Object getText() {
043      return text;
044   }
045
046   /**
047    * Sets the inner text of this element.
048    *
049    * @param text The inner text of this element, or <jk>null</jk> if no text is set.
050    * @return This object.
051    */
052   @Beanp("c")
053   public HtmlElement setText(Object text) {
054      this.text = text;
055      return this;
056   }
057
058   /**
059    * Sets the text node on this element.
060    *
061    * @param text The text node to add to this element.
062    * @return This object.
063    */
064   @FluentSetter
065   public HtmlElement text(Object value) {  // NOSONAR - Intentional naming.
066      this.text = value;
067      return this;
068   }
069
